PrecisLEAST DEVELOPED DEVELOPING COUNTRIES ORDER (ANGOLA, ERITREA AND BOTSWANA) which extends the Least Developed Developing Countries (LDDC) tariff treatment to General Preferential Tariff (GPT) eligible imports from ANGOLA and ERITREA and withdraws LDDC tariff treatment from GPT eligible imports from BOTSWANA.
